operation.expression: 'SELECT bo_prdct_mstr_xref1.PKEY_SRC_OBJECT AS ITEM_SKEY, BO_PRDCT_LNKNG_XREF.LNK_TYP AS LINK_TYPE, bo_prdct_mstr_xref2.PKEY_SRC_OBJECT AS LINK_SKEY, CASE WHEN BO_PRDCT_LNKNG_XREF.HUB_STATE_IND = ''-1'' THEN ''Y'' ELSE ''N'' END AS HUB_STATE_IND FROM MATERIALS_HUB.C_BO_PRDCT_LNKNG_XREF BO_PRDCT_LNKNG_XREF INNER JOIN MATERIALS_HUB.C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF bo_prdct_mstr_xref1 ON bo_prdct_mstr_xref1.ROWID_XREF = BO_PRDCT_LNKNG_XREF.PRDCT_MSTR_FK_1 INNER JOIN MATERIALS_HUB.C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF bo_prdct_mstr_xref2 ON bo_prdct_mstr_xref2.ROWID_XREF = BO_PRDCT_LNKNG_XREF.PRDCT_MSTR_FK_2 WHERE BO_PRDCT_LNKNG_XREF.last_update_date> TO_TIMESTAMP('',$temp.vTemp_DateFilter , ''',',',''DD-MM-YY HH24:MI.SSXFF')'

fn:concat('SELECT C_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF.PKEY_SRC_OBJECT AS ITEM_SKEY, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.PCKNG_UNT AS PACKING_UNIT, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.IAN AS EAN_UPC_NUMBER, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.GRSS_WGHT AS GROSS_WEIGHT, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.NT_WGHT AS NET_WEIGHT, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.UNT_WGHT AS WEIGHT_UNIT_OF_MEASURE, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.VLM AS VOLUME, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.VLM_UNT AS VOLUME_UNIT_OF_MEASURE, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.PCKNG_WDTH AS PCKNG_WDTH, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.PCKNG_HGHT AS PCKNG_HGHT, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.PCKNG_LNGTH AS PCKNG_LNGTH, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.PCKNG_VLM AS PCKNG_VLM, C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.PCKNG_UNT_FOR AS PCKNG_UNT_FOR FROM ', $temp.vTempSchema ,'.', $temp.vTempC_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF , ' INNER JOIN ', $temp.vTempSchema,'.', $temp.vTemp_C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF , ' ON ', $temp.vTempSchema ,'.', $temp.vTempC_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF,'.ROWID_XREF = ', $temp.vTempSchema,'.', $temp.vTemp_C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF , '.PRDCT_MSTR_FK WHERE C_BO_PRDCT_LGSTC_XREF.last_update_date> TO_TIMESTAMP('',$temp.vTemp_DateFilter , ''',',',''DD-MM-YY HH24:MI.SSXFF')' )

(:Agregar Alias al query y formato a la fecha YYYY-MM-DD HHMMSS:) fn:concat('SELECT xref.PKEY_SRC_OBJECT AS ITEM_SKEY, mstr.MTRL_IDNTFR AS PRODUCT_IDENTIFIER, mstr.OVRLL_MTRL_TYP AS OVERALL_ITEM_TYPE, mstr.MTRL_TYP AS ITEM_TYPE, mstr.CHAMP_CD AS CHAMP_CODE, mstr.PRDCT_CTGR AS PRODUCT_CATEGORY, mstr.TCHNLG_GRP AS TECHNOLOGY_GROUP, mstr.PRDCT_HRCHY AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY, mstr.PRDCT_TYPE AS PRODUCT_TYPE, mstr.BS_UNT_MSR AS BASE_UNIT_OF_MEASURE, mstr.DVSN AS BU, mstr.SBU_DVSN AS SBU, mstr.STATUS_CD AS PRODUCT_STATUS, mstr.ORGNTNG_ID AS ORIGINATING_IDENTIFIER, mstr.SRC_SYSTM_ID AS ORIGINATING_SYSTEM, mstr.NW_PRDCT_LNCH_DT AS NEW_PRODUCT_LAUNCH_DATE, mstr.ITM_EXST_SRC AS ITEM_EXISTS_IN_SOURCE, mstr.CREATOR, to_Char(mstr.CREATE_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS') as CREATE_DATE, mstr.UPDATED_BY, to_Char(mstr.LAST_UPDATE_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS') as LAST_UPDATE_DATE FROM ', $temp.vTempSchema ,'.', $temp.vTempC_BO_PRDCT_MSTR,' mstr',' INNER JOIN ',$temp.vTempSchema ,'.', $temp.vTempC_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF,' xref ON MSTR.ROWID_OBJECT = xref.ROWID_OBJECT AND mstr.SRC_SYSTM_ID = xref.SRC_SYSTM_ID WHERE xref.ROWID_SYSTEM <> 'SYS0' AND mstr.last_update_date > TO_TIMESTAMP('',$temp.vTemp_DateFilter , ''',',',''DD-MM-YY HH24:MI.SSXFF')' )

(:Agregar Alias al query y formato a la fecha YYYY-MM-DD HHMMSS:) fn:concat('SELECT xref.PKEY_SRC_OBJECT AS ITEM_SKEY, xref.MTRL_IDNTFR AS PRODUCT_IDENTIFIER, xref.OVRLL_MTRL_TYP AS OVERALL_ITEM_TYPE, xref.MTRL_TYP AS ITEM_TYPE, xref.CHAMP_CD AS CHAMP_CODE, xref.PRDCT_CTGR AS PRODUCT_CATEGORY, xref.TCHNLG_GRP AS TECHNOLOGY_GROUP, xref.PRDCT_HRCHY AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY, xref.PRDCT_TYPE AS PRODUCT_TYPE, xref.BS_UNT_MSR AS BASE_UNIT_OF_MEASURE, xref.DVSN AS BU, xref.SBU_DVSN AS SBU, xref.STATUS_CD AS PRODUCT_STATUS, xref.ORGNTNG_ID AS ORIGINATING_IDENTIFIER, xref.SRC_SYSTM_ID AS ORIGINATING_SYSTEM, xref.NW_PRDCT_LNCH_DT AS NEW_PRODUCT_LAUNCH_DATE, xref.ITM_EXST_SRC AS ITEM_EXISTS_IN_SOURCE, xref.CREATOR, to_Char(xref.CREATE_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS') as CREATE_DATE, xref.UPDATED_BY, to_Char(xref.LAST_UPDATE_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS') as LAST_UPDATE_DATE FROM ', $temp.vTempSchema ,'.', $temp.vTempC_BO_PRDCT_MSTR,' mstr',' INNER JOIN ',$temp.vTempSchema ,'.', $temp.vTempC_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF,' xref ON MSTR.ROWID_OBJECT = xref.ROWID_OBJECT WHERE xref.ROWID_SYSTEM <> 'SYS0' AND xref.last_update_date> TO_TIMESTAMP('',$temp.vTemp_DateFilter , ''',',',''DD-MM-YY HH24:MI.SSXFF')' )

fn:concat('SELECT C_BO_PRDCT_HRCHY_XREF.PKEY_SRC_OBJECT AS ITEM_SKEY, MTRL_IDNTFR AS PRODUCT_IDENTIFIER, PRDCT_HRCHY_L1 AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_L1, PRDCT_HRCHY_L2 AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_L2, PRDCT_HRCHY_L3 AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_L3, PRDCT_HRCHY_L4 AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_L4, PRDCT_HRCHY_L5 AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_L5, PRDCT_HRCHY_L6 AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_L6, PRDCT_HRCHY_N1 AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_N1, PRDCT_HRCHY_N2 AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_N2, PRDCT_HRCHY_N3 AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_N3, PRDCT_HRCHY_N4 AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_N4, PRDCT_HRCHY_N5 AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_N5, PRDCT_HRCHY_N6 AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_N6, PRDCT_HRCHY_ID AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_ID, PRDCT_HRCHY_NM AS PRODUCT_HIERARCHY_NAME, LANG_KEY AS LANGUAGE_KEY
FROM ', $temp.vTempSchema,'.', $temp.vTempC_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF, ' INNER JOIN ', $temp.vTempSchema,'.', $temp.vTempC_BO_PRDCT_HRCHY_XREF, ' ON ', $temp.vTempSchema ,'.', $temp.vTempC_BO_PRDCT_MSTR_XREF,'.ROWID_XREF = ', $temp.vTempSchema,'.', $temp.vTempC_BO_PRDCT_HRCHY_XREF, '.PRDCT_MSTR_FK WHERE C_BO_PRDCT_HRCHY_XREF.last_update_date> TO_TIMESTAMP('',$temp.vTemp_DateFilter , ''',',',''DD-MM-YY HH24:MI.SSXFF')' )
